item.title: How to make new outfit and changing home?
item.dc:creator: @LOLMFAO LOLMFAO
item.description:
@LOLMFAO wrote:

okay this is actually very simple what you need to do is make a totally new account and login this is very important do NOT MOVE!!! now open up client.java and search for your x coord replace it with the new xcoord save now search for the ycoord you’re standing on and replace it with the one you want do so save and close now open up player.java or it might be playerhandler im not 100% sure well anyways search for the id’s of shit you’re wearing and replace like the hat id with w/e hat or helmet you want etc. and while you’re in there search for the x and y coords and replace them save, close and compile restart your server and you’re set to go
